    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "change_id": "6b5a4f0d-d72d-4bb4-8476-052707ba9bf5",
      "node_type": "observation",
      "title": "MapSystem.wasm fails wasm-validate with huge clusters of errors. Dominant patterns: (1)  expects a value but stack is empty => dropping void or earlier stack corruption; (2)  expects i32 args but stack is empty => missing pushes / wrong expression emission; (3) i32 ops fed f32 and vice versa => missing/incorrect coercions or wrong typed op selection; (4) local index out of range suggests locals declared don't match indices used (likely relooper state/local mapping).",
      "description": null,
      "status": "pending",
      "created_at": "2026-01-26T15:33:21.560202-05:00",
      "updated_at": "2026-01-26T15:33:21.560202-05:00",
      "metadata_json": "{\"branch\":\"main\",\"confidence\":90}"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "change_id": "eecb10a2-77a5-4d46-af8a-4f6bad9a34fd",
      "node_type": "observation",
      "title": "MapSystem.wasm validator errors cluster around: (1) \"type mismatch in drop, expected [any] but got []\" (drop of void / empty stack); (2) \"type mismatch in call, expected [...] but got []\" (missing args due to broken emission); (3) i32.* ops receiving f32 and f32.* ops receiving i32 (missing/incorrect IRValue.convert or op selection); (4) block/return result mismatches (returning from non-void without value); (5) local index out-of-range (locals declared vs referenced mismatch, possibly relooper state local).",
      "description": null,
      "status": "pending",
      "created_at": "2026-01-26T15:33:29.193830-05:00",
      "updated_at": "2026-01-26T15:33:29.193830-05:00",
      "metadata_json": "{\"branch\":\"main\",\"confidence\":92}"
    },
